OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,FNow Guernsey's Committee for Policy
OL,7,Fand Resources (P&R) want new proposals
OL,8,Fto widen the runway debated in the
OL,9,FStates by February, with the hopes of
OL,10,Fgetting spades in the ground by early
OL,11,F2027.
OL,13,FIn 2024, the previous P&R
OL,14,Fadministration scrapped their plans
OL,15,Ffor Alderney's runway after costs
OL,16,Fballooned from an agreed #24.1 million
OL,17,Fbudget to #37 million.
