OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,FAt the time, P&R called the proposals
OL,7,F"unviable and unaffordable", despite
OL,8,Fdisappointment from Alderney's
OL,9,Fpoliticians and hospitality leaders.
OL,11,FThese new proposals - earmarked for a
OL,12,Fmaximum budget of #24 million - will
OL,13,Fsee the runway widened from 18 to 23
OL,14,Fmetres, keeping its current length of
OL,15,F877 metres.
OL,17,F"It's essential for Alderney to have
OL,18,Fan operational runway, and it really
OL,19,Fis as simple as that," Deputy Lindsay
OL,20,Fde Sausmarez, President of P&R, told
OL,21,FITV News.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
