OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,F"We have committed to bringing in this
OL,7,Fproject at the lowest possible cost
OL,8,Fwithout cutting corners on things like
OL,9,Fsafety or regulatory standards.
OL,11,F"At the end of the day, infrastructure
OL,12,Fprojects like these are inherently
OL,13,Fexpensive, but they also need to be
OL,14,Fdone."
OL,16,FThe proposed scheme will reconstruct
OL,17,Fthe asphalt runway, with the widening
OL,18,Fallowing the runway to meet the needs
OL,19,Fof Code B aircraft, such as the Twin
OL,20,FOtter aircraft that currently uses the
OL,21,Frunway.
