OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,FPlans also include resurfacing work,
OL,7,Frealigning the main asphalt taxiway,
OL,8,Finstalling modern drainage, and
OL,9,Fupdating the airfield lighting systems
OL,10,Fto reduce disruption during bad
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,FThe States of Guernsey has warned that
OL,14,F"extensive groundworks" will also
OL,15,Fimpact the future of the two existing
OL,16,Fgrass runways.
