OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,FBoth are used by private aircraft, but
OL,7,Fworks may mean the longer runway may
OL,8,Fbe permanently closed, while the
OL,9,Fshorter one will be retained for an
OL,10,Falternative access to the main runways.
OL,12,FHowever, unlike the scrapped plans,
OL,13,Fthe runway will not be extended, and
OL,14,Fthere are no plans to build a new
OL,15,Fterminal.
OL,17,FDespite this, States of Alderney's
OL,18,FPolicy & Finance Committee said they
OL,19,F"fully support" the proposals.
