OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,FDuring work, Alderney Airport may need
OL,7,Fto be closed for an extended period
OL,8,Fwhile work is underway.
OL,10,FStates of Guernsey have stated that
OL,11,Fresidents will be given prior notice
OL,12,Fand will be directed to alternative
OL,13,Ftravel options.
OL,15,FProvision for emergency medical
OL,16,Fevacuations will still be available.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
