OL,3,C#24 million plans for Alderney runway
OL,4,Cupgrades proposed
OL,6,F"We look forward to working closely
OL,7,Fwith (P&R) and the States Trading
OL,8,FSupervisory Board to ensure best value
OL,9,Fis achieved, and the project is
OL,10,Fdelivered as soon as practicable,"
OL,11,FPolicy & Finance Committee Chairman
OL,12,FBill Abel stated.
OL,14,F"This engagement will also focus on
OL,15,Fminimising the impact of closures and
OL,16,Fevaluating viable options to minimise
OL,17,Fthe risk of closure of the grass
OL,18,Frunways, taking into consideration
OL,19,Foverall benefits to the island."
